column2: SELECT TOP # PZ1.z, P1.ra, P1.dec, PZ2.z,P2.ra, P2.dec FROM Photoz as PZ1,  Photoz as PZ2,  Neighbors as NG,  PhotoObj AS P1,  PhotoObj AS P2 Where PZ1.ObjID = NG.ObjID   and PZ2.ObjID = NG.NeighborObjID   and NG.distance < #/#  and PZ1.z BETWEEN # and #  and PZ1.ObjID =P1.ObjID  and PZ2.ObjID =P2.ObjID
